25\/30 na traseira e 315\/30 na dianteira completam o conjunto.\n\nUma prepara\u00e7\u00e3o feita e assinada pelos amigos do \u0040gz28br gerando n\u00fameros surreais de pot\u00eancia: 1.140cv e e 118kgfm de torque!\n\nThe Alpha Snake:\n\nR$ 1.380.000,00\n\n*Para mais infos, acesse nosso site ou consulte-nos.\n_______________________________\n\nVia Bella, h\u00e1 29 anos no mercado!\nO carro deixa com a gente.\n_______________________________\n#shelby #gt500 #mustang #carporn #supercar"},"__isNode":"Video","creation_story":{"click_tracking_linkshim_cb":"AT7ZbHcC5jg6YvlaL_QJS3eKiOgBoTVEabPjqoE8kQ6U6y7NvYGhAe4nRBKLvJ0Kh3ILWNoDvMjrvPQ1fXuBD5z1-f3ANK72RrHIRMUxdeBBLt1N7QAfYKcgJ9sEluaBE4bKL7KM55-IaaF02oMljIB09-rozqyuXsbywkqMQUh79U6DPTJm","encrypted_click_tracking":"AZZAdaaa-uFIBE3fyR4qsz6kM1151g0QrLpO_hV2W40jiW8lysXd8atsLmKqiUJvK6VfvVP2_o4-bCY__ql5Pv1DA_Ancw6OX4vrIgAG9youdpLLs0WNXkd9Z3NTJsNeeEWcFm4VgIOM65139hHaTwAzwsUXBrxd-or3HsPAk4m7Pg","encrypted_tracking":"AZaVFIiHnRqYJSD1p2a5-TLPqMQ15N2pfw4NuCevk4ypSTXKAbyDmPAE1g5kbocJUlJ3EF4eLVtYvARd8mTKHI8JqTFEVSdey8oUab9It_JU-QvPElZ1RQJ3ETsr00Fn4tOV-MXHhfsRLgIapcGrIuM9yTNTxq4ALzXO9ILICHhO2pjj99KXMcq1SD4rlQ5mZ06KNqMKf-MYJuxZMTHSgoo3FvZ6YERdo00_d5evsazWMaucGKip8N81_tYMH85Lw31pztbnTMy99HXC4CBNDo11MhTW8HeTHMdw5caKhFLSlHNXU9Vxp8FAByYBLiJ2LUJa_LvvvmyHVU0lbJ9q_OS5qkf-Iez_jdC6QWNJhlORBldq4brD45Qv8kIw0h2BGWj0qpYhtpHVIocw2Dn6XbLf5z18Y0nLF0tM8DfMyly3W24Rs82J6_GBzcfaWNMC-4KPkbjBeKghawu4q02nkIOEo6W3D6hk9uZ8ZlcSv_fys6fvWDP87CuNo7JTQ-lc5kPOq7lcbkHNCf5nZymnUeAENKuNff1aOppr74bKyeNFtxr2hRB8gW6BLIsg_-RzXiOOkd2c4Pwv6opxYF0za5C8KLM050lk-u3UrOaGU2U2R0uk4sZTVKQVq_WrEg_G_zf_dyg_GSGp03R2Le3Lxe4K83f8IHo6O3mC15tZRU1iJwQaNnbkkX2oeeK0wMeJYSAI_NgB_AiV393KIlXvIOe0ue7JFV8gDkxXMdINIPi_7Xl15YBecykmionmYfvCJOvaNjjkZ7yHd3xLWN_rgN3zcy87ceWvK2XStRp9hYo5hyNIQUXvIS07aJkxpjACvLBZmMyxQarDRYMVjiwflTp6kXqzunQjstzJi0Ir5UZnBCD1IeVSBBeSDVdvadhR0BRdB00dZLH75SyVfIMyaFJsJJI7JoRbcADQoCgbQ5YCl2VXuVxxsO7Vzt4twklYTGe4jxf4YT1Yfq3rFEE-QABpL6f2LvVa_h-HpunFTSond0GTFPPVUWn353Mg9pDtwFBDtnb